      "inquiry_widget_no_score_no_reveal_no_a": "Inquiry widget — no score, no reveal, no answer dump. T = √(a³/M) per Kepler III with M in solar masses, a in AU, T in years. Vis-viva used for v at perihelion / aphelion.",
